modName: World of Warcraft Weapons and Armor Pack
summary: A pack of high quality weapons and armor. These textures WERE NOT created by me I simply felt that those who like to download less and want all the best stuff, they could just download a single convenient file. All credit goes to the creators below.
descriptionHtml:
These Amazing Weapons and Armors are created by John Skyrim, AthenaX, LuciferX10, Faxivcm, Crazy Lion and the optional file if you are interested was created by CelsiuZ and Hellscreamy. CelsiuZ and Hellscreamy created a great world that looks great and it is of course a WIP but non the less it still looks good at its current stage.
